Prominent 5 Level CBD building located in the popular eastern end of the CBD with areas from 240-1,700sqm available from early 2019. 

With a caf on the ground floor and other employee amenities in close proximity, 139 Frome Street provides a terrific offering to the marketplace.

With full fitouts in place and side core access, the following area are available for lease:

- Ground Floor of 350 sqm*
- Whole Level 2 of 731sqm*
- Whole Level 3 of 731sqm*
- Part Level 4 (North) of 240sqm*

Natural light is provided from 3 sides with pleasant views over the City Beach complex.

Signage and ample basement car parking are available subject to negotiation.

Contact the agents today to view this quality CBD offering

A Boutique Hutt Street property that is located in the commercial heart of the eastern CBD precinct.

Featuring the whole of the ground floor, 153 Hutt Street provides a terrific opportunity for the small business to occupy a well-lit tenancy that is both self contained and well presented.

102 square metres in size, the layout is flexible and efficient and allows a small-medium tenant to occupy without any fuss.

Signage opportunities are available (STC) plus one (1) on-site car park.

*approx

This stunning 2-level office building with basement parking provides a high level of office accommodation. The property was recently refurbished including a new impressive ground floor lobby and finishes throughout. 

The building is prominently located on the Eastern side of Frome Street, between Pirie and Flinders Streets, and enjoys 3-street frontage.

A fantastic tenancy on the first floor of approximately 545sqm is now available for lease in this popular eastern side CBD building.

It lies in very close proximity to Rundle Street East, and has at its door step, an outstanding array of restaurants, cafes, wine bars, hotels, cinemas and retail shops.

The perfect location for staff to enjoy the working environment and for clients to visit with ease given the abundancy of on-street parking adjacent to the building.

This space has all the hallmarks of clean, modern, boutique commercial accommodation.

Other features of this quality offering include:
- Well presented tenancy comprising offices, boardroom, 55 + work-stations, storage, IT room, large kitchen / staff break out etc ready for occupation
- Terrific natural light throughout with floor-to-ceiling windows on all three sides
- Lift and stair access from basement up to Level 1
- Ten (10) valuable on-site undercover and secure car parks
- Prominent building signage opportunities available

This would be one of the best boutique office spaces of its kind in the City centre going around.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Fantastic mix of the old and the new!

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
If you are looking for something different from the standard office building, here it is.  Fully refurbished, 199 Rundle Street Adelaide provides a high level of office accommodation with a great mix of the old and the new.  

Featuring fantastic high ceilings, polished floorboards, good natural light and views over Rundle Street, it is afforded with full lift access to the floor and a modern entrance/lobby area.

Comprising 205 square metres approx* on level 1, the tenancy is both flexible, secure and on-trend and will appeal to a myriad of users with its open-plan layout.

Available immediately, please contact the exclusive agents to inspect.

Located on the Paris-end of Flinders Street in the Aqua Apartment building, this architecturally designed, self-contained office suite at 270 Flinders Street has it all.

Direct lift access to some 60sqm (approx.) of open plan space with floor to ceiling glass windows, kitchenette together with your own private balcony

The tenancy is afforded with a workstation layout that compliments the tenancy with a new toilet recently installed. 

1 on-site carpark available with the tenancy.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Fully fitted out boutique office space

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: SUPERB OFFICE SPACE THAT DELIVERS STYLE AND SOPHISTICATION

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Superbly fitted out space of 251 sqm

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A beautifully maintained and presented office space that will make coming to work a genuine pleasure.

Located directly above popular East End eateries, Toyama Japanese and Mum Cha, this level one space comprise a large open reception/waiting area, boardroom, two meeting rooms/offices, several partitioned offices, open plan work areas, store, kitchen/staff breakout and its own recently upgraded male and female bathrooms and shower amenities.

The space is presented at its charming best with a combination of polished timber floors and sleek charcoal-colored carpets, and enjoys high ceilings.  The natural lighting is just perfect, and is beautifully accentuated throughout with modern, glass-dividing walls.  The layout could easily allow your business to sub-lease individual offices.

Situated on Rundle Street East, you will have Adelaides best coffee and dining experiences at your door step including Lemongrass, Ong Vietnamese Kitchen, Eros Kafe, La Taberna, Golden Boy, Africola, Exchange, Hey Jupiter, Felici Espresso Bar, The Laneway on Ebenezer, Siciliy e Pizzeria, Yiasou George, etc.  And Friday night drinks have never looked better  think Mothervine, East End Cellars, NOLA, The Exeter, Mr Goodbar, The Stag Public House, The Belgian, Hellbound, etc.

Other surrounding commercial and corporate offices include KWP!, Shaw Lawyers, Leyton Property, JL Lawyers, Cox Architecture, CEDA, Society Marcom, Viva Energy, MT Lawyers, FYI Docs, Lanyon Asset Management, Ekistics Planners, MPH Architects, and many more.   

A truly spectacular office in Adelaides most vibrant, mixed-use City precinct.
